{"word":"G3340 - μετανοέω - metanoéō - met-an-o-eh'-o - Repent","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">μετανοέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">metanoéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">met-an-o-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Repent</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - மனந்திரும்பு, மனஸ்தாபப்படு"},{"paragraph":"to change one's mind, to repent"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G3326 - μετά - metá - met-ah'/3326\">G3326</a> and <a href=\"#/G3539 - νοιέω - noiéō - noy-eh'-o/3539\">G3539</a>; to <i>think differently</i> or <i>afterwards</i>, that is, <i>reconsider</i> (morally to <i>feel compunction</i>): - repent.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1270/1270\">G1270</a>, <a href=\"#/G1271/1271\">G1271</a>, <a href=\"#/G1425/1425\">G1425</a>, <a href=\"#/G1771/1771\">G1771</a>, <a href=\"#/G2132/2132\">G2132</a>, <a href=\"#/G2133/2133\">G2133</a>, <a href=\"#/G2657/2657\">G2657</a>, <a href=\"#/G279/279\">G279</a>, <a href=\"#/G3340/3340\">G3340</a>, <a href=\"#/G3539/3539\">G3539</a>, <a href=\"#/G3540/3540\">G3540</a>, <a href=\"#/G3559/3559\">G3559</a>, <a href=\"#/G3563/3563\">G3563</a>, <a href=\"#/G4306/4306\">G4306</a>, <a href=\"#/G4307/4307\">G4307</a>, <a href=\"#/G453/453\">G453</a>, <a href=\"#/G454/454\">G454</a>, <a href=\"#/G5282/5282\">G5282</a>, <a href=\"#/G5283/5283\">G5283</a>"}]}